data.description: Conveniently located, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home built in 2019! On the main floor, you will find an open kitchen, breakfast area and great room as well as a separate dining room and half bath. All bedrooms, laundry and full baths are located upstairs including a spacious master suite with a walk-in closet and private bathroom. Minutes from Robins AFB and downtown Macon! Do not miss this one!!
